<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
     <meta charset="UTF-8">
     <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
     <title>Selamat Datang di Sales AIDIA</title>
     <!-- Google Fonts: Plus Jakarta Sans -->
     <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
     <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
     <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
          rel="stylesheet">
     <style>
          * {
               margin: 0;
               padding: 0;
               box-sizing: border-box;
          }

          body {
               font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
               line-height: 1.6;
               color: #333333;
               background-color: #f4f4f4;
          }

          .email-wrapper {
               max-width: 600px;
               margin: 0 auto;
               background-color: #ffffff;
          }

          .header {
               background: black;
               padding: 40px 30px;
               text-align: center;
          }

          .header h1 {
               color: #ffffff;
               font-size: 28px;
               font-weight: 600;
               margin: 0;
          }

          .content {
               padding: 40px 30px;
          }

          .greeting {
               font-size: 18px;
               color: #333333;
               margin-bottom: 20px;
          }

          .message {
               font-size: 15px;
               color: #666666;
               margin-bottom: 30px;
               line-height: 1.7;
          }

          .credentials-box {
               background-color: #f8f9fa;
               border-left: 4px solid black;
               padding: 20px;
               margin: 30px 0;
               border-radius: 4px;
          }

          .credentials-box h3 {
               color: #333333;
               font-size: 16px;
               margin-bottom: 15px;
               font-weight: 600;
          }

          .credential-item {
               margin: 12px 0;
               font-size: 14px;
          }

          .credential-label {
               color: #666666;
               font-weight: 500;
               display: inline-block;
               width: 100px;
          }

          .credential-value {
               color: #333333;
               font-weight: 600;
               font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
               background-color: #ffffff;
               padding: 4px 8px;
               border-radius: 3px;
               display: inline-block;
          }

          .cta-button {
               display: inline-block;
               background: black;
               color: #ffffff;
               text-decoration: none;
               padding: 14px 32px;
               border-radius: 6px;
               font-weight: 600;
               font-size: 15px;
               margin: 20px 0;
               transition: transform 0.2s;
          }

          .cta-button:hover {
               transform: translateY(-2px);
          }

          .info-box {
               background-color: #fff9e6;
               border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
               padding: 15px;
               margin: 20px 0;
               border-radius: 4px;
          }

          .info-box p {
               font-size: 13px;
               color: #856404;
               margin: 0;
          }

          .footer {
               background-color: #f8f9fa;
               padding: 30px;
               text-align: center;
               border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
          }

          .footer p {
               font-size: 12px;
               color: #999999;
               margin: 8px 0;
          }

          .footer-links {
               margin: 15px 0;
          }

          .footer-links a {
               color: #667eea;
               text-decoration: none;
               font-size: 12px;
               margin: 0 10px;
          }

          .meta-info {
               font-size: 13px;
               color: #999999;
               margin-top: 30px;
               padding-top: 20px;
               border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
          }

          .meta-info-item {
               display: inline-block;
               margin: 5px 15px 5px 0;
          }

          @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
               .header {
                    padding: 30px 20px;
               }

               .header h1 {
                    font-size: 24px;
               }

               .content {
                    padding: 30px 20px;
               }

               .credential-label {
                    display: block;
                    margin-bottom: 5px;
               }

               .credential-value {
                    display: block;
               }
          }
     </style>
</head>

<body>
     <div class="email-wrapper">
          <!-- Header -->
          <div class="header">
               <h1>Sales AIDIA</h1>
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="content">
               <p class="greeting">Halo, <strong>{{userName}}</strong>!</p>

               <p class="message">
                    Selamat datang di <strong>Sales AIDIA</strong>. Akun Anda telah berhasil dibuat dan siap digunakan.
                    Berikut adalah kredensial login Anda:
               </p>

               <!-- Credentials Box -->
               <div class="credentials-box">
                    <h3>ðŸ“§ Kredensial Login Anda</h3>
                    <div class="credential-item">
                         <span class="credential-label">Email:</span>
                         <span class="credential-value">{{userEmail}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="credential-item">
                         <span class="credential-label">Password:</span>
                         <span class="credential-value">{{generatedPassword}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="credential-item">
                         <span class="credential-label">Role:</span>
                         <span class="credential-value">{{roleName}}</span>
                    </div>
               </div>

               <!-- CTA Button -->
               <center>
                    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-button">Login ke Sales AIDIA</a>
               </center>

               <!-- Security Info -->
               <div class="info-box">
                    <p>
                         <strong>ðŸ”’ Tips Keamanan:</strong>
                         Kami sangat menyarankan Anda untuk mengubah password ini setelah login pertama kali
                         melalui menu Pengaturan Akun.
                    </p>
               </div>

               <!-- IT Support Contact -->
               <div
                    style="background-color: #e8f4f8; border-left: 4px solid #0288d1; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
                    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #01579b; margin: 0;">
                         <strong>ðŸ’¬ Butuh Bantuan?</strong><br>
                         Jika mengalami kendala dalam penggunaan sistem, silakan hubungi Tim IT kami melalui WhatsApp:
                         <a href="https://wa.me/6287789765911"
                              style="color: #0288d1; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">+62 877-8976-5911</a>
                    </p>
               </div>

               <!-- Meta Info -->
               <div class="meta-info">
                    <div class="meta-info-item">
                         <strong>Dibuat:</strong> {{createdAt}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-info-item">
                         <strong>Status:</strong> Aktif
                    </div>
               </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <div class="footer">
               <p><strong>Sales AIDIA</strong></p>
               <p>Sistem Manajemen Penjualan Terintegrasi</p>

               <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
                    Email ini dikirim secara otomatis oleh sistem Sales AIDIA.<br>
                    Mohon tidak membalas email ini.
               </p>
          </div>
     </div>
</body>

</html>